{"about_the_game":"<strong>OVERVIEW</strong><br>A Christmassy Christmas is an Arena Roguelike Survival game where Santa is on a rampage wiping out the population of Naughty Children. Wield the reins as Santa, in a dance of survival so vital. His duty, a twisted chore, fight to keep the legend alive evermore.<br><br>Christmas may be over, but Santa still needs your help! Come and play to keep the festive spirit alive and assist Santa in fulfilling his sacred duties.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745400/extras/menupress__2_.gif?t=1729026571\" /><br><br><strong>UPGRADES</strong><br><br>Santa is not one to go into battle unprepared. After collecting enough Souls of the Naughty Children, Santa can repurpose them as a source of power. The Souls fuel Santa's Magic, allowing him to summon more powerful attacks of his choice. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745400/extras/upgradesfeature.gif?t=1729026571\" /><br><br><strong>CROSS OFF ALL NAUGHTY NAMES</strong><br><br>In the abyss where Naughty deeds persist, Endure until each name is crossed off the list. Eternally erased, in shadows they twist, Fates sealed in darkness, a final tryst.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2745400/extras/basicenemyfeature.gif?t=1729026571\" /><br><br><strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong><br><br><i>Keyboard &amp; Mouse</i><br>WASD or Arrow Keys to move.<br>LEFT SHIFT or SPACE to dash! <br>Use your mouse or touchpad to select upgrades or menu items. <br><br>Your goal as Santa is to survive for 10 minutes, this may sound easy, but the government will throw everything they have at you in order to take Santa down, including their super secret weapon...<strong> Mecha-Santa...</strong><br><br>Very few have survived an encounter with Mecha-Santa, and even less have killed him. <br><br><strong>SAVING PROGRESS!</strong><br><br>This game supports saving! After a round of playing, you can purchase permanent upgrades that will auto save when you close the app. <br><br><strong>ENJOY!</strong><br><br>I hope you find plenty of enjoyment going down this dark road as Santa. I am a solo indie dev practicing Game Design. Feedback &amp; Suggestions are always appreciated.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"You Actually Played!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/8b89241cc8d3c570f3387b0d2390a5e259d0704e.jpg"},{"name":"Maximum Power!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/c82c356c0b909196292ae5ad3a851e505da8857c.jpg"},{"name":"Survivor!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/048882d2a495446acbc15f5194bad3b8b0f60751.jpg"},{"name":"UNSTOPPABLE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/08ff0b4d739e94f708364ad40cc375d7736ab2c4.jpg"},{"name":"Mecha-Santa Slayer!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/5e6f7f2f78adb5b2b991f83d8c66d3ff528c524c.jpg"},{"name":"Soul Hoarder!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/0c28f86fbd21997a8a891df613fd076d83d75bfe.jpg"},{"name":"Over 9000!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/061dbef1bf91ffea5386f4b51e06328b16d74e42.jpg"},{"name":"Elf Airstrike!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/fb6f7fe386e8c605cfe60e8e2d51cde761efbb8f.jpg"},{"name":"The Frost God","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/832f95fb2ef2cb8fd1edde98c8f747b6c0655dfa.jpg"},{"name":"HAPPY HALLOWEENY","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2745400/b04f7a8458e8da9c851ef4dfea6be9bd2fc356e0.jpg"}],"total":10},"background":"https://s